data.description: Spacious 5 Bedroom, 3 Full Bath Home in the Heart of Chelsea! Freshly Painted and Immaculately Maintained! Open concept kitchen, den, and dining area are perfect for entertaining. Kitchen features an oversized island, granite countertops and walk-in pantry. Corner gas fireplace for cozy living. Main level bedroom with private full bath is perfect for guests or as an office. Oversized master suite with seating area, large walk-in closet, and spa-like bathroom. Three additional bedrooms are complemented by a full bath. Covered back patio extends indoor-outdoor living with a fully fenced yard that backs to woods for privacy. What else will you love about this home? The upstairs loft area, the large laundry room, and spacious double garage with storage galore. Swim Community! Walk to Publix and Las Mesas Mexican Cantina! Within minutes to all the shopping and dining Chelsea has to offer!
